short_description: Lamination equipment differs according to the types of material to be processed. But this US-ZD-FMF105-1000 model laminating machine can laminate both woven and non-woven materials and even paper. The total power of the equipment is 60 kW, the weight is 5500 kg, the length is 13 m, the width is 8 m and the height is 2.5 m. Below are other models and they differ in price and parameters.

Ammo ushbu US-ZD-FMF105-1000 modeldagi laminatsiya qilish uskunasi to'qilgan va to'qilmagan materiallarni ham va hatto qog'ozni ham laminatsiya qila oladi. Uskunaning umumiy quvvati 60 kW, vazni 5500 kg, uzunligi 13 m, kengligi 8 m va balandligi 2.5 m. Quyida boshqa modellar ham bor va ular narxda hamda parametrlarda farqlanadi.
